                <li>Regional users step – select one store from the store selection list.</li>
                <br />
                <img src="/Content/images/Support/Select Store Custom Report.JPG" />
                <li>Select one or multiple Teams (hold down the CTRL key for multiple selections).</li>
                <br />
                <img src="/Content/images/Support/Select Team Custom Report.JPG" />
                <li>Select one or multiple Sub Teams.</li>
                <br />
                <img src="/Content/images/Support/Select Subteam Custom Report.JPG" />
                <li>Select the Generate Report button.</li>
                <br />
                <img src="/Content/images/Support/Generate Report Custom Report.JPG" />
                <li>Select Open from the prompt (this will open the report in Excel).</li>
                <br />
                <img src="/Content/images/Support/Open File.JPG" />
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="question" id="question">
        <p class="lead">
            <a href="#answer8" onclick="toggleAnswer('answer8')">What are the data sources of the Custom Report?</a>
