            <a href="#answer14" onclick="toggleAnswer('answer14')">How do I edit multiple Product Status?</a>
        </p>

        <div class="answer" id="answer14" style="display: none">
            <ul class="answer">
                <li>Perform a search to display the items you want to edit.</li>
                <br />
                <img src="/Content/images/Support/Search Product Status.JPG" />
                <li>Select the check box next to the items you want to edit.</li>
                <br />
                <img src="/Content/images/Support/Edit Mutiples Product Status.JPG" />
