    <div class="question" id="question">
        <p class="lead">
            <a href="#answer15" onclick="toggleAnswer('answer15')">How do I remove a single Product Status?</a>
        </p>

        <div class="answer" id="answer15" style="display: none">
            <ul class="answer" >
                <li>From the Product Status tab, select the green Search button.</li>
                <br />
                <img src="/Content/images/Support/Search Product Status.JPG" />
                <li>You may search by entering a Status, UPC, Expiration Date, or all.</li>
                <li>Select the Search button to begin your search.</li>
                <br />
                <img src="/Content/images/Support/Click Search Product Status.JPG" />
                <li>To delete an item, select the Remove icon.</li>
                <br />
                <img src="/Content/images/Support/Single Remove Status Product Status.JPG" />
